Both of them should be there.

122
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:35,160
Is there anything dirty behind me?

123
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,000
- Alright.
- I'm telling you.

124
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:39,560
That circular part on that machine.

125
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,200
Action.

126
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,720
You'll just stay there, huh?

127
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,360
Trying to peek at me, huh?
Peek at me as you please, then!

128
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,360
Did I scratch you?

129
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,560
Do I close this?

130
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,040
One, two, three!

131
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,680
Pull it! Okay.

132
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,000
Alright.

133
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,320
They've all been lying to me!

134
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,440
Kiss me!

135
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,720
Have you lost your mind?

136
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,520
Hold her hand. There's no space here.

137
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,520
Each of them has a face.

138
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,320
You see the bathtub.

139
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:22,080
- Okay. Let's give it a try.
- Alright.

140
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,000
Well, normally,

141
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,100
you'll walk by and take a glimpse.

142
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,400
Yeah, that's it.

143
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,320
Slow down.

144
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,640
Bite her.

145
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,320
That hurts!

146
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,840
Now, you're Chi Yu.

147
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,440
Just kiss her.

148
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,120
That's right.

149
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,520
You stop here.

150
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,800
Be gentle. Go slow.

151
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,360
Here, ready. Hyah!

152
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,400
The heels definitely won't fit.

153
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,560
The heels won't fit.

154
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:48,800
