155
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,320
- Use some oil, then.
- Hahaha! Let's just use some oil.

156
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:54,040
Yeah, you could turn around. That's it.

157
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,520
Do I do it myself?

158
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,120
Who did this?

159
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,320
They stepped on the dress. And she fell.

160
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,440
Just once. Yeah.

161
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,840
Face him this way.

162
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,560
He will take two steps back.

163
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:45,560
Use this gesture. And push it!

164
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,640
Thank you all for your hard work.

165
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,960
