May Twin Fates be a popular show!

169
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,440
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

170
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,960
Do you have anything to say?

171
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,920
I'm happy

172
